{
  "texts": [
    "Developing a user-friendly interface that would let consumers easily access the AI's offerings was a key component of this phase.",
    "This includes integrating conversational AI tools & chatbots into the main dashboard of the site so users may quickly ask questions or request help.",
    "The MCO conducted thorough user testing using a sample population of Medicaid & Dual members before the AI system's release.",
    "The comments from this testing stage helped the system to be improved by ensuring that the AI generated responses for members were clear, more relevant, and also more practical.",
    "The assessment also pointed out areas of the AI system that need improvement, like adjusting the response tone to show greater empathy and adding more data for certain therapeutic settings."
  ]
}